                    { 8753, "", "24 min per ep", new DateTime(1992, 5, 23, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 26, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/1353/136492.jpg", 9003, "PG - Children", 6.15m, 3, 6, new DateTime(1991, 11, 16, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 1, "The Ultraman Kids are a lovable bunch of outer space kids on a quest through the galaxy to find their leader Mar's missing parents. Along the way they have fun and adventures and even learn a thing or two!\n\nMar is the leader of the Ultraman Kids. He's a curious fun-loving little boy with a taste for adventure and a talent for mischief. Mar is still learning how to use his fantastic Ultra Powers so sometimes his Ultra Beam goes everywhere except where he's aiming. Look out! Together these kids find fun and adventure wherever they go. \n\n(Source: Amazon)", "Ultraman Kids: Haha wo Tazunete 3000-man Kounen", "Ultraman Kids: 30 Million Light-Years in Search of Mother", "ウルトラマンキッズ 母をたずねて3000万光年", null, 1, "https://myanimelist.net/anime/8753/Ultraman_Kids__Haha_wo_Tazunete_3000-man_Kounen" },
