                    { 9040, "", "13 min per ep", new DateTime(2010, 12, 18, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 3, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/13/25033.jpg", 6595, "G - All Ages", 6.56m, null, 1, new DateTime(2010, 8, 14, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 1, "Haru Irei, who witnessed the 1/1 scale RX-78-2 Gundam in Odaiba, becomes inspired to build Gunpla, which is a portmanteau of Gundam Plastic model kit. Haru purchases a one of a kind gunpla, the GPB-X80 Beginning Gundam. After building the kit, Haru, now a Gunpla Builder, and the Beginning Gundam enter the virtual world of Gunpla Battle, where players can pilot their customized Gunpla in team matches or one-on-one fights. Haru must rely on the support of his friends if he is to become a Gunpla Battle Champion and attain the rank of Gunpla Meister.", "Mokei Senshi Gunpla Builders Beginning G", null, "模型戦士 ガンプラ ビルダーズ ビギニングG", null, 4, "https://myanimelist.net/anime/9040/Mokei_Senshi_Gunpla_Builders_Beginning_G" },
