                    { 19759, "", "31 min", null, 1, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/8/52773.jpg", 3444, "PG-13 - Teens 13 or older", 7.18m, null, 2, new DateTime(2013, 10, 5, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 1, "Class 3-E is getting ready for their class trip to Kyoto, and Koro-sensei is as excited as ever! Nagisa is in a group with Kaede, Karma, Tomohito, Manami, and the class idol Yukiko Kanzaki. The students are aware of the fact that this is a great opportunity to assassinate Koro-sensei, but they cannot help having great time with him. However, the trip becomes even more exciting and dangerous when they get attacked by a bunch of delinquents who kidnap the girls. As if that is not enough, there is a hired sniper named Red Eye lurking around, ready to be the one who would assassinate Koro-sensei and claim the prize. Can the students of Class 3-E rely on Koro-sensei even now?", "Ansatsu Kyoushitsu: Jump Festa 2013 Special", "Assassination Classroom: Jump Festa 2013 Special", "暗殺教室", null, 4, "https://myanimelist.net/anime/19759/Ansatsu_Kyoushitsu__Jump_Festa_2013_Special" },
