                    { 31050, "Cyborg 009 VS Devilman is a crossover anime which was announced separately as new works of Cyborg 009 (in March 2015) and Devilman (in April 2015). The two were later revealed to be a single work. It was screened in theaters for a two-week period beginning October 17, 2015, before being released as OVAs. Ishimori Production co-sponsored the production as part of the 50th anniversary of the Cyborg 009 manga.", "31 min per ep", null, 3, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/1985/121991.jpg", 8333, "R - 17+ (violence & profanity)", 6.27m, null, 2, new DateTime(2015, 11, 10, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 1, "After discovering the existence of demons in Tokyo, the original Cyborg crew led by Dr. Gilmore find themselves in conflict with Devilman, a strong demon believed to be in league with the war-profiteering terrorist organisation, Black Ghost. Meanwhile, a bigger threat emerges when Dr. Adams, a Black Ghost scientist unleashes his new line of high teen Cyborg models against 009 and his friends.\n\n(Source: ANN)", "Cyborg 009 VS Devilman", null, "サイボーグ009VSデビルマン", "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JJGtwXtNqRw", 3, "https://myanimelist.net/anime/31050/Cyborg_009_VS_Devilman" },
                    { 31051, "", "23 min", null, 1, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/13/77323.jpg", 523, "PG-13 - Teens 13 or older", 8.09m, null, 2, new DateTime(2015, 12, 23, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 1, "It is Tetsuya Kuroko's birthday. In celebration, Satsuki Momoi has invited the other members of the Generation of Miracles to play basketball together and rekindle the memories from their nostalgic middle school days. Meanwhile, Taiga Kagami and his fellow teammates of Seirin High are doing their best to prepare for Kuroko's birthday party.\n\nSometimes, the best gift one can receive is not a material one but, rather, the feeling of having fun with everyone!\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Kuroko no Basket: Saikou no Present desu", "Kuroko’s Basketball: It is the Best Present", "黒子のバスケ〜最高のプレゼントです〜", "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=h9WOHL4N0e4", 4, "https://myanimelist.net/anime/31051/Kuroko_no_Basket__Saikou_no_Present_desu" },
