                    { 31133, "Featuring animation not seen in the television series, Shounen Sunday CM Gekijou: InuYasha-hen are two commercials for the Shounen Sunday magazine. The first was made around the time that the InuYasha manga debuted and the other slightly prior to the anime's premiere. The earlier commercial used voice actors different from those in the anime broadcast.", "32 sec per ep", new DateTime(2000, 10, 15, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/13/74768.jpg", null, "PG-13 - Teens 13 or older", 6.22m, null, 2, new DateTime(1996, 11, 12, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 1, "In an age of turmoil, a tenacious couple comes together amid dire adversities: they are the reckless half-demon Inuyasha and his spirited human companion Kagome Higurashi.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Shounen Sunday CM: InuYasha-hen", "InuYasha: Shounen Sunday CM", "少年サンデー CM劇場 「犬夜叉編」", null, 8, "https://myanimelist.net/anime/31133/Shounen_Sunday_CM__InuYasha-hen" },
