                    { 35000, "To LOVE-Ru: Multiplication - Mae kara Ushiro kara was bundled with the book To Love-Ru Chronicle, which was released for the 10th anniversary of the franchise.", "12 min", null, 1, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/3/87158.jpg", 3621, "R+ - Mild Nudity", 7.14m, null, 2, new DateTime(2017, 11, 1, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 1, "On what would typically be another ordinary day, Lala Satalin Deviluke takes one of her recent inventions—a robotic cat with cloning powers—to school for a chance to show it to Rito Yuuki. Upon accidentally touching the gadget, Rito begins repeatedly duplicating himself, and the school is soon entirely overrun by a horde of his clones.\n\nThe only way to deactivate the cat is to hold its tail; however, its agility makes this a challenge. Will Rito's army of himself be able to catch it, or will the Earth be flooded by an unstoppable wave of duplicates?\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "To LOVE-Ru: Multiplication - Mae kara Ushiro kara", null, "To LOVEる -とらぶる- Multiplication ~前から後ろから~", null, 3, "https://myanimelist.net/anime/35000/To_LOVE-Ru__Multiplication_-_Mae_kara_Ushiro_kara" },
