                    { 35311, "", "1 min", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/11/85034.jpg", 18819, "G - All Ages", null, null, 1, new DateTime(2009, 11, 4, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Kamiusagi Rope and TOHO Cinemas collaboration episodes that were released online only.", "Kamiusagi Rope x TOHO Cinemas", null, "紙兎ロペ TOHOシネマズ", null, 6, "https://myanimelist.net/anime/35311/Kamiusagi_Rope_x_TOHO_Cinemas" },
                    { 35312, "", "2 min", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/11/85035.jpg", 18820, "G - All Ages", null, null, 1, new DateTime(2014, 1, 10, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Kamiusagi Rope episodes for TOHO Cinemas that aired between theater commercials. Most are collaborations or advertisements and they are not considered to be a part of the movie series (ie. Kamiusagi Rope, Kamiusagi Rope 2, Kamiusagi Rope 3) due to being advertisements as well as having an irregular releases.\n\nSome were shown at all TOHO Cinemas (eg. Kashiwa was shown everywhere to advertise the new Kashiwa TOHO Cinemas opening the following month) while others were regional restricted (eg. Hissawwaza was shown only in TOHO Cinemas Shinjuku in honor of the theater's grand opening as well as being a collaboration with the Godzilla franchise and Tokyo Metro's new IC Touch campaign).\n\nNone of these episodes were released online at a later date nor included in any DVD release of Kamiusagi Rope.", "Kamiusagi Rope x TOHO Cinemas (Movies)", null, "紙兎ロペ TOHOシネマズ", null, 2, "https://myanimelist.net/anime/35312/Kamiusagi_Rope_x_TOHO_Cinemas_Movies" },
