                    { 41306, "An animated video shown at the 2004 Tokyo International Anime Fair, serving as a pilot to the 2007 JoJo's Bizarre Adventure: Phantom Blood film. The video consists of scenes directly adapted from the manga, with unique footage not present in the film. The pilot also has different character designs and events compared to the final product.", "2 min", null, 1, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/1704/106122.jpg", 6150, "R - 17+ (violence & profanity)", 6.64m, null, 2, new DateTime(2004, 3, 27, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 1, "A 2-minute animated video highlighting key points in the battle between the courageous Jonathan Joestar and his adoptive brother Dio Brando, who has turned into a powerful vampire.", "JoJo no Kimyou na Bouken: Phantom Blood Pilot", "JoJo's Bizarre Adventure: Phantom Blood Pilot", "ジョジョの奇妙な冒険 ファントム ブラッド", null, 4, "https://myanimelist.net/anime/41306/JoJo_no_Kimyou_na_Bouken__Phantom_Blood_Pilot" },
