                    { 53588, "", "1 min", null, 1, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/1889/130946.jpg", 5213, "PG-13 - Teens 13 or older", 6.81m, null, 3, new DateTime(2022, 11, 5, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 1, "Opening video for the \"Sword Art Online -FULLDIVE-\" event which took place at the Tokyo Garden Theater. This memorial event was to celebrate 10 years of the Sword Art Online anime, with an original story by Reki Kawahara performed by the anime's seiyuus via live voice drama and musical guest performances by artists involved with the anime's music throughout the decade.\n\nThe animation shows the main characters of the Aincrad Arc right before they put on the NerveGear and begin their fateful adventure in the Sword Art Online game.\n\n(Source: Anime News Network, edited)", "Sword Art Online: Full Dive - Opening Eizou", "Sword Art Online: Full Dive - Opening Video", "「ソードアート・オンライン -フルダイブ-」オープニング映像", null, 2, "https://myanimelist.net/anime/53588/Sword_Art_Online__Full_Dive_-_Opening_Eizou" },
                    { 53590, "Saijaku Tamer wa Gomi Hiroi no Tabi wo Hajimemashita. was released on Blu-ray on June 5, 2024.", "23 min per ep", new DateTime(2024, 3, 28, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 12, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/1280/138474.jpg", 1714, "PG-13 - Teens 13 or older", 7.56m, 4, 3, new DateTime(2024, 1, 11, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 1, "Born into a loving family, Femicia appears to have a bright future ahead of her. When she finally turns five, the time comes to go to the church to have her skills appraised. However, while she does receive a monster tamer skill, it turns out that Femicia has zero stars for that ability. To make matters worse, society considers those who have zero stars to be harbingers of misfortune; as a result, Femicia is shunned by everyone—including her family.\n\nSoon enough, Femicia is chased out of her village and is constantly on the run. Fearing for her life, she decides to masquerade as a boy and change her name to Ivy. With a goal given to her by a fortune teller to reach the royal capital, Ivy meets and successfully tames a slime, starting an unlikely friendship that may provide a means to get the destiny she deserves.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Saijaku Tamer wa Gomi Hiroi no Tabi wo Hajimemashita.", "The Weakest Tamer Began a Journey to Pick Up Trash", "最弱テイマーはゴミ拾いの旅を始めました。", "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LtwLjXQ3p1A", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/anime/53590/Saijaku_Tamer_wa_Gomi_Hiroi_no_Tabi_wo_Hajimemashita" },
